    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2685269/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2685269-19.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2685269/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">titaic</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-19"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-19 12:15:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5220453_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  基本上遇到德国部分我就有阅读障碍，不知是翻译原因，我本身理解问题还是作者的写作手法，看到德国部分我就云里雾里。大致读出来的印象就是，德国人唯恐把纳粹批判地不彻底，唯恐把纳粹当做人来看，因为仿佛这样就可以把他们从歌德席勒的德国里剥离出来。而日本的情况则不同，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            博雅書屋2010版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5220453_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5220453_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评7篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
